name: Bing Bing
description: Bing Bing is an innovative fashion e-commerce platform that uses Web3 technology and Internet Computer Protocol (ICP) to enhance the online shopping experience. In Bing Bing, users are able to upload their image to the platform, where our advanced virtual try-on technology overlays the selected fashion items onto the uploaded photos, allowing them to see how the items would look on them before making a purchase.

name: Binder
description: Binus Tinder is a dating app made for BINUS University students. With its flagship feature of matchmaking through video calls and authentication using BINUS' email, it ensures the authenticity of profiles and promotes safer interactions among its users, fostering a community where students can connect across campus and create meaningful relations.

name: Artemis
description: Artemis is an event management platform to help BINUS University's SLC division schedule and manage its many appointments. It is created to help streamline and centralize scheduling, to help officers and staffs check available schedules, room usage, and send appointment emails through the use of Microsoft Graph API.
